{
  "stem": "11274.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't go from one town to the other one visiting-- visiting somebody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we couldn't earn a living.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we couldn't-- with the farmers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the stores, I think, were still open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The kosher butcher was still open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we couldn't have-- later on, they forbid that, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We couldn't have-- go buy in-- for money in the store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But if I made-- if you made something or did something for the Gentile-- so my sister Zosia was-- escaped with a little boy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He needed tonsils removed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was already scheduled at the doctor, and they wouldn't allow it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had a guy, like I had later, and they brought her to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had it done, the surgery done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she remained in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had two children at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, I want to stay back before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to ask you when you weren't in school, summers for example, did you have any jobs that you did?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in grade school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After grade school, after grade school, I went to extended education courses they were offering because there was no official high school there-- or gymnasium it's called there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the, the teachers, the local teachers, arranged from all the schools, from the two schools, that thought if somebody-- there were some people didn't know how to read and write.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was for the elderly who didn't know how to read and write.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was for the one who wanted to advance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like I finished the seventh grade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my teacher kept me for one more year, to the eighth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was a little bit-- 14-- older than the other children.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
